<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Bid Rejected</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f44336;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .auction-details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f44336;
        }
        .rejected-amount {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #f44336;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>‚ùå Bid Rejected</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{buyerName}},</h2>
        
        <p>We regret to inform you that the seller has decided not to accept your bid for the following auction.</p>
        
        <div class="auction-details">
            <h3>Auction Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Item:</strong> {{auctionTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Auction ID:</strong> #{{auctionId}}</p>
            <p><strong>Seller:</strong> {{sellerName}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="rejected-amount">
            Your Bid: ${{rejectedAmount}}
        </div>
        
        <p>While this particular transaction didn't work out, we encourage you to continue participating in our auctions. There are always new and exciting items being listed!</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for your participation and we look forward to seeing you in future auctions.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The AuctionBid Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from AuctionBid Platform</p>
        <p>Explore more auctions on our platform!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
